data.description: Located in the highly desirable Heights at Two Creeks, this 4 bdrm & 3 1/2 bath features an open floor plan with built-in keypad front door, arched entry, beautiful iron railing staircase, & home office with hardwood and tile floors. The kitchen features 42-inch cabinets, gas cooking, granite counters, mosaic backsplash, and recessed lighting. Iron railing staircase. Primary bedroom downstairs with bay window, walk-in closet. The Master Bath features dual vanities, granite, tub & shower. Huge upstairs secondary bedroom with full bathroom. Don't forget the water sprinkler, water softener, & epoxy garage flooring, and NEW ROOF. Exemplary NISD Schools! Schedule your showing today!
